column5: Hey Brian Happy B-Day just think if yer were born in july we could have gone musky fishing for the day well we will just have to make a date for then anyway. Hope ya had a good one
Hope you're having a great day, Slowpoke! Happy Happy to ya.
Happy Birthday Brian ! Have a great evening....
Happy Birthday Brian!!!  I hope you had a great day and got everything you wished for!!!   Bly
Happy Birthday Brian,sounds like a swill may need to be planned,enjoy whats left of your day. Brian
Happy Birthday Brian my fellow teamate.Team #4   .Celebrate your birthday by catching a huge Trout in your new boat.
One minute to post a happy B-day to you  jjcanoe

Don't worry guys he's got a trip all planned out for this Saturday.  (maiden voyage of the S.S. Slowpoke)  and a happy B-day again Brian,  White truck, what's next white hair?  (like I should talk!)  jjcanoe

Thanks everyone!  Kind of a crappy day... only saw my family for about ten minutes in the morning... spent the day running around wasting time and spending money and my b-day meal was a Chicken Caeser Salad at McDonalds around 11PM. The highlight of my day was getting an extra packet of salad dressing. Fortunately the family and I celebrated last weekend... cake.. fishing toys.. hugs & kisses etc.  JJ, as for white hair? I just hope to have hair at all in a couple more years!
